  "title": "Prime Mover Driver",
  "description": "<p>[1:23 PM, 1/29/2026] Joey M. SIM (SGI): Job Description:</p><p>The Prime Mover Driver is responsible for the safe and timely transportation of containers, ISO tanks, and other cargo between ports, warehouses, and customer locations within Singapore. The role requires strict compliance with traffic regulations, company safety policies, and port authority requirements while ensuring cargo integrity and on-time delivery.</p><p></p><p>Key Responsibilities:</p><p>Operate prime mover vehicles to transport containers, ISO tanks, and bulk cargo safely</p><p>Collect and deliver cargo to and from PSA ports, warehouses, and customer sites</p><p>Conduct pre-trip and post-trip vehicle inspections and basic maintenance checks</p><p>Ensure proper securing of containers and compliance with safety procedures</p><p>Complete delivery documentation and report any discrepancies or incidents</p><p>Adhere to LTA, MOM, and port safety regulations at all times</p><p></p><p>Requirements:</p><p>Valid Singapore Class 4 or Class 5 driving licence</p><p>Minimum relevant driving experience preferred</p><p>Familiarity with PSA port operations and routes in Singapore</p><p>Good safety awareness and responsible driving attitude</p><p>Physically fit and able to work flexible hours or shifts</p><p></p>",
